{"tid":524777,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LG示範AI產品換來沉默回應","createTime":"2018-01-10T02:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T03:44:50.000Z","uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"316ff327aea183f5e010a192d3829b6715ab8dcd","tid":524777,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"今年消費電子展另一個特點是多間公司展出應用人工智能技術的產品，但是南韓電器生產商LG展示新研發人工智能系統時卻遇上了尷尬場面。<br />\n<br />\nLG展示的智能語音機械人，預設是可以控制公司其他應用人工智能系統的電器。<br />\n<br />\n不過在示範期間，公司高層查問洗衣機設定、食譜及預訂晚餐時，機械人都表現沉默，令場面非常尷尬，LG未有解釋出錯原因。<br />\n<br />\n有觀看現場直播的網民則開玩笑指，系統可能是女性並對在廚房被男性指指點點感到不滿，決定不予配合。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=249856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D249856&d=wbybNbZG5TiC%2FlbXGPiTWMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=91512602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D249856&h=30d36197\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=249856</a>"},{"pid":"03690e63c4f5d56574acfd517598acc8be76240a","tid":524777,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部可能想答你今晚食自己,但費事佢尷尬,所以唔出聲,,,已經証明有AI"},{"pid":"eed3118c8028b9293910c63947bae95eb09b927c","tid":524777,"uid":44333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴辣雞粒</span>"},{"pid":"6e7b9384af14bb2c53b5701239dc98672069c263","tid":524777,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed3118c8028b9293910c63947bae95eb09b927c","tid":524777,"uid":44333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴辣雞粒</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no